Grammar

    0 $accept: Program $end

    1 Program: Decls

    2 Decls: Decls Decl
    3      | ε

    4 Decl: FuncDecl
    5     | VarDecl
    6     | TypeDecl

    7 FuncDecl: VarType IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ParamList RPARENTHESES SEMICOLON
    8         | VarType IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ParamList RPARENTHESES FuncBody

    9 FuncBody: LBRACE Stmts RBRACE

   10 VarDecl: VarType VarList SEMICOLON
   11        | VarType IDENTIFIER LBRACKET INTEGER RBRACKET SEMICOLON

   12 TypeDecl: _VarType SEMICOLON

   13 VarType: _VarType
   14        | CONST _VarType

   15 _VarType: BuiltinType
   16         | STRUCT IDENTIFIER LBRACE FieldDecls RBRACE
   17         | UNION IDENTIFIER LBRACE FieldDecls RBRACE
   18         | ENUM IDENTIFIER LBRACE EnumList RBRACE
   19         | _VarType ASTERISK
   20         | IDENTIFIER

   21 VarList: VarList COMMA VarInit
   22        | VarInit
   23        | ε

   24 VarInit: IDENTIFIER
   25        | IDENTIFIER ASSIGN Expr

   26 ParamList: ParamList COMMA Param
   27          | ParamList COMMA ELLIPSES
   28          | Param
   29          | ELLIPSES
   30          | ε

   31 Param: VarType IDENTIFIER
   32      | VarType

   33 BuiltinType: CHAR
   34            | SHORT
   35            | INT
   36            | LONG
   37            | UNSIGNED
   38            | UNSIGNED CHAR
   39            | UNSIGNED SHORT
   40            | UNSIGNED INT
   41            | UNSIGNED LONG
   42            | FLOAT
   43            | DOUBLE
   44            | BOOL
   45            | VOID

   46 FieldDecls: FieldDecls FieldDecl
   47           | ε

   48 FieldDecl: VarType MemberList SEMICOLON
   49          | SEMICOLON

   50 MemberList: MemberList COMMA IDENTIFIER
   51           | IDENTIFIER
   52           | ε

   53 EnumList: EnumList COMMA Enum
   54         | Enum
   55         | ε

   56 Enum: IDENTIFIER
   57     | IDENTIFIER ASSIGN INTEGER

   58 Stmts: Stmts Stmt
   59      | ε

   60 Stmt: Expr SEMICOLON
   61     | IfStmt
   62     | SwitchStmt
   63     | ForStmt
   64     | DoStmt
   65     | WhileStmt
   66     | ContinueStmt
   67     | BreakStmt
   68     | ReturnStmt
   69     | Block
   70     | TypeDecl
   71     | VarDecl
   72     | SEMICOLON

   73 IfStmt: IF LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt ELSE Stmt
   74       | IF LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

   75 SwitchStmt: SWITCH LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES LBRACE CaseStmtList RBRACE

   76 CaseStmtList: CaseStmtList CaseStmt
   77             | ε

   78 CaseStmt: CASE Expr COLON Stmts
   79         | DEFAULT COLON Stmts

   80 ForStmt: FOR LPARENTHESES Expr SEMICOLON Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt
   81        | FOR LPARENTHESES SEMICOLON Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt
   82        | FOR LPARENTHESES VarDecl Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

   83 DoStmt: DO Stmt WHILE LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES SEMICOLON

   84 WhileStmt: WHILE LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

   85 ContinueStmt: CONTINUE SEMICOLON

   86 BreakStmt: BREAK SEMICOLON

   87 ReturnStmt: RETURN SEMICOLON
   88           | RETURN Expr SEMICOLON

   89 Block: LBRACE Stmts RBRACE

   90 Expr: IDENTIFIER
   91     | Constant
   92     | LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES
   93     | Expr COMMA Expr
   94     | IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ExprList RPARENTHESES
   95     | Expr DOT IDENTIFIER
   96     | Expr ARROW IDENTIFIER
   97     | Expr LBRACKET Expr RBRACKET
   98     | LPARENTHESES VarType RPARENTHESES Expr
   99     | SIZEOF LPARENTHESES VarType RPARENTHESES
  100     | SIZEOF LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES
  101     | SIZEOF LPARENTHESES IDENTIFIER RPARENTHESES
  102     | ADD Expr
  103     | SUB Expr
  104     | ASTERISK Expr
  105     | AMPERSAND Expr
  106     | Expr ASSIGN Expr
  107     | Expr ADD Expr
